48
00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:53.440
Growing apart is one of the most frequently given reasons for divorce.

49
00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:59.280
And eventually Marina and her husband's problems became unresolvable, not able to be fixed

50
00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:01.840
