There was an interesting thing they did in China where they introduced this cooling off period.

60
00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:41.480
So the government enforced this.

61
00:03:41.480 --> 00:03:47.600
Does that work when the government intervenes in a situation like this and makes people behave

